QuestData.Title: Lost Lumberjack
QuestData.Description: Me friend was in the mole machine wit' me. Good ol' Frenna tried to make the best of it by writin' all o' her observations down in a journal.$b$bPenny here wants me to tell ya where she is. I cannae say for sure, but she was followin' me outta here and I don't think she made it.
QuestData.RewardText: Frenna didn't make it out of Tangleheart.
